=== Precinct shrines ===
* Kotohira Shrine
* Hachiman Shrine
* Tsushima Shrine
* Yamagami Shrine

=== Festivals ===
* Monthly festival: every month on the 7th
* Jan 1 - New Year Festival
* Jan 14 - Sagichō Festival
* Mar 7 - Kinen Festival
* Jul 7 - Chinowa Festival
* Aug 7 - Annual Grand Festival
* Oct 7 - Prayer Festival
* Dec 7 - Niiname Festival
* Dec 30 - Great Purification Festival

=== Access ===
* {{ill|lt=Nagoya Municipal Subway|Q1144874|WD=Q1144874|1=Nagoya Municipal Subway}}{{ill|lt=Meijō Line|Q906775|WD=Q906775|lt=Meijō Line|1=Meijō Line}} - about 10 minutes on foot from Exit 2 of {{ill|lt=Meijō Kōen Station|Q863874|WD=Q863874|1=Meijō Kōen Station}}.
* {{ill|lt=Nagoya Municipal Bus|Q11414982|WD=Q11414982|1=Nagoya Municipal Bus}} - get off at "Jōhokubashi" on Sakae 11 / Sakae 25 routes, about 5 minutes on foot.

